verses.roman:
rāmānanda-rāya tabe gelā nija ghare
svarūpa-govinda duṅhe śuilena dvāre

synonyms: rāmānanda-rāya—Rāmānanda Rāya; tabe—thereupon; gelā—returned; nija ghare—to his home; svarūpa—Svarūpa Dāmodara Gosvāmī; govinda—and Govinda; duṅhe—both; śuilena—lay down; dvāre—at the door.
translation: Then Rāmānanda Rāya returned home, and Svarūpa Dāmodara Gosvāmī, along with Govinda, lay down in front of the door to Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu's room.
